47 technicians employed by the crematory licensee providing that nothing in this Article shall
48 prohibit the designation and identification by the crematory licensee of one individual to serve
49 as a crematory manager and crematory technician. Each crematory licensed in North Carolina
50 shall employ on a full-time basis at least one crematory technician. Every application for
