7 PART V. RULEMAKING AND EFFECTIVE DATE
8 SECTION 5.1. The North Carolina Board of Funeral Service may adopt temporary
9 rules to implement the provisions of this act. Temporary rules adopted in accordance with this
10 section shall remain in effect until permanent rules that replace the temporary rules become
11 effective.
12 SECTION 5.2. Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
13 law.
